## D. Generalized Workspace Boundary
- Work only inside the approved workspace path.
- Do not inspect, copy, modify, delete, commit, deploy, or infer from sibling/reference projects unless explicitly approved in the current slice.
- Sibling/reference projects include:
	- folders next to approved workspace;
	- prior websites used as inspiration;
	- template/source/reference repos;
	- production websites;
	- old experiments;
	- unrelated client/internal projects.
- Nếu AG đụng sibling/reference project mà chưa duyệt: `STOP / RECOVER`.
- Nếu AG xin đọc reference project: `BLOCKED / needs explicit reference-read approval`.
