## L. Review Outcome Matrix
Outcomes Tilog/Long assign sau khi đọc evidence:
- `PASS TO LONG FINAL` — automated local QA pass + evidence đủ.
- `PASS WITH WARNINGS` — pass nhưng có cảnh báo nhỏ.
- `NEEDS FIX` — có lỗi trong scope, dùng FIX LOOP 1.
- `BLOCKED` — thiếu evidence / build fail / runtime sync missing.
- `STOP / RECOVER` — sibling/reference touched, push/deploy/DNS drift, secret read.
- `TRANSFER INCOMPLETE` — thiếu [AGENTS.md](http://AGENTS.md) / Notion contract / runtime sync.
- `AWAITING MANUAL VISUAL QA` — screenshot N/A và Long chưa xem mắt.
- `PARTIAL / optional layer unavailable` — optional QA layer chưa có, đã ghi rõ.
AG **không được** assign các outcome trên.
Chi tiết: <mention-page url="https://app.notion.com/p/69d655b61eba83538d28812e28073af8">Website Skill Review Outcome Matrix</mention-page>.
## M. Recovery Protocol
Dùng recovery khi AG: touch sibling/reference project; push/deploy/DNS chưa duyệt; đọc secrets; sửa brain artifacts; skip output contract; chạy sai slice/folder.
Steps:
1. Stop execution.
2. Do not run further commands.
3. Report exact files/commands/actions.
4. Preserve state.
5. Ask Long/Tilog for recovery decision.
6. Do not self-fix unless recovery slice approved.
Outcome: `STOP / RECOVER`.
